{"tid":1396734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"現在正式徵用[活動台]作為[任務台]！！！","createTime":"2019-08-02T07:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:18:37.000Z","uid":42691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19057b1ba56a8788de64012d3432475f16bba9ee","tid":1396734,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:50:03.000Z","msg":"(唔好意思頭先柒咗)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>現況</ins></strong><br />\n吹水台太多post 容易沉底<br />\n導致好多任務類型既post要不斷自推<br />\n浪費好多手足既時間<br />\n而想幫手做任務既巴打又遇唔到呢類post<br />\n結果有心做既冇得做 想做既遇唔到<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>提議</ins></strong><br />\n將部份任務類型post 開係活動台<br />\n好似打機咁 活動台就係你既任務清單<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">現在正式徵用活動台作為任務台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>任務類型舉例</ins></strong><br />\n1.[聯署]禁狗移民去美國<br />\n2.[檢舉]檢舉fb點相post<br />\n3.[推post]幫手推呢個post<br />\n4.[要人]馬鞍山要人<br />\n5.[登報]急求兩個排版手足<br />\n6.[尋片]求昨晚所有一手片<br />\n7.[投訴]三個步驟投訴tbb<br />\n8.[起底]幫手起xxx 有任何資料 發送到此新電郵<br />\n9.[夾錢]登報/手術費&hellip;<br />\n10. ..............<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>注意事項</ins></strong><br />\n1.活動台內只會有任務列表<br />\n盡量不作任何討論 一旦陷入討論 就要追post <br />\n追追下就冇人想做 <br />\n2.係其他台討論完 整理好先入活動台開post<br />\n3.未整理好既post 麻煩幫手負皮<br />\n想巴絲幫手做任務 就清楚列明任務要求 <br />\n唔好入到去先傾先研究<br />\n記住內文越簡潔清楚 越少討論 越方便巴絲做任務<br />\n甚至部份任務可以俾非會員做<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>最後</ins></strong><br />\n每做完一個 左手邊就會有紅點 <br />\n未做就誠實消除回帶<br />\n可以大概統計你為香港做咗幾多貢獻<br />\n加上我發現巴絲開始有懶散跡象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望呢個任務清單台可以鼓勵多d人做任務<br />\n要懶既 贏咗再慢慢懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輸咗既話 我地將會活在地獄 永不超生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313df4eee01585bddce49df92f45fc63d3073858","tid":1396734,"uid":42691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:50:37.000Z","msg":"原來黑洞開唔到post<br />\n歡迎恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705e403103fb6790e046b420f7f66ea20e68ab52","tid":1396734,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:51:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4fce10366d240d1456e55aaec93d96f24c24ed","tid":1396734,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d44e550c15ed00a744b67114ee2f5ca5bc3f6aa","tid":1396734,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:08:31.000Z","msg":"入去睇完指引  開去活動台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n指示越清楚越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好一樓就可以做任務<br />\n說明呀背景呀個d可以擺二樓"},{"pid":"c7a1eb35f62374ef6a3c050741e4bf062365729a","tid":1396734,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">活動台 = 任務清單</span></span>"},{"pid":"8f212d0f54fdda6ea4fa67e84f6811b7d7553439","tid":1396734,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:28:24.000Z","msg":"已經有兩個例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[聯署] 日本政府話香港人=中國人，係香港人就入來簽名<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396940</a><br />\n<br />\n[聯署] 阻止曾偉雄被任命為聯合國維也納辦事處總幹事！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396951</a>"},{"pid":"6d91279bb1224290f7e91db2148de2003082675b","tid":1396734,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f20a9a11d0ec06dc824c07c5b570a0c1276e4de","tid":1396734,"uid":259515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:49:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1a434a42b6033f65e60c5423600aa713cc8f6beb","tid":1396734,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9d6fad8a0e89036dbde77d362a3d6072ceee4fd","tid":1396734,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:44:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"820c69a9486715508ef584f9fb9dd66568c0f64f","tid":1396734,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:18:37.000Z","msg":"推"}]}